              <h4>Based on your household size and income, you likely do not qualify for Rental Assistance.</h4>

              <br>

            <div class="row">
              <p class="subhead">The financial assistance program provides essential relief services to persons in need of shelter, food, utility payments, medication and other items. Contact Emergency Fund directly at (312) 379-0301 for rent assistance.
