            <div class="row">
            <p class="subhead">The Chicago Housing Authority Waitlist Lottery registration is open now through Nov. 24 for the three types of housing opportunities: Public Housing, Housing Choice Voucher (Tenant-Based Voucher or Section 8) and Property Rental Assistance (Project-Based Voucher). Online registration is free, and easy to use. The registration form will be available in several different languages.</p>
            <%= link_to "Click Here", "www.thechawaitlist.org", :class => "btn btn-success btn-resolution" %>
            <p class="subhead">or call 312.971.7700 for more information.</p>

          </div>





